  "title" : "Java.Lang.IllegalArgumentException .NET MAUI",
  "body" : "<p>After installing BarcodeScanner.Mobile version 8.0.0.1 I get this exception when the application starts: <code>MAUI Java.Lang.IllegalArgumentException: 'This component requires that you specify a valid TextAppearance attribute. Update your app theme to inherit from Theme.MaterialComponents (or a descendant).'</code></p>\n<p>Does anyone got the same experience?</p>\n"
